					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5585680#post-3748688</guid>
				<title>GAZE UPON THE REWRITE</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5585680/scp-2651#post-3748688</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 25 Mar 2018 00:08:38 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>NatVoltaic</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2800867</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>A while back I wrote SCP-2651, which ended up having some people enjoy it while flopping tremendously as far as votes go. For a while I was unhappy with how it turned out, wondering if I could do something to improve it, then recently I figured out stuff that could work. Here's the article with that new stuff.</p> <p>Note that a mystery is intentional here. I don't expect everyone to know exactly what's happening (the details for figuring out most of it are there, though).</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">However,&nbsp;there&nbsp;is&nbsp;one&nbsp;part&nbsp;I'm&nbsp;fine&nbsp;with&nbsp;spoiling(?)</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">hide&nbsp;spoiler(?)</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>This alien species was trying to colonize Earth.</p> </div> </div> </div> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/maliceaforethought" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2902864&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521936871" alt="MaliceAforethought" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2902864)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/maliceaforethought" >MaliceAforethought</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521936871" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" >DarkStuff</a></span> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=776854&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521936871" alt="Tanhony" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=776854)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" >Tanhony</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3187823&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521936871" alt="CadaverCommander" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3187823)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" >CadaverCommander</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3208919&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521936871" alt="taylor_itkin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3208919)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taylor-itkin" >taylor_itkin</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521936871" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" >Captain Kirby</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1553042&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521936871" alt="PeppersGhost" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1553042)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/peppersghost" >PeppersGhost</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2727655&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521936871" alt="Weryllium" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2727655)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/weryllium" >Weryllium</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1229263&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521936871" alt="Roget" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1229263)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/roget" >Roget</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3337265&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521936871" alt="Tufto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3337265)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" >Tufto</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kakroom" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2198340&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521936871" alt="Kakroom" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2198340)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kakroom" >Kakroom</a></span> for crit! Special thanks to everyone that helped with the original draft and left feedback once it was posted.</p> <p>Image source:</p> <ul> <li>(first drawing made by myself and released under the Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0 license)</li> <li><a href="https://pixabay.com/en/cave-tunnel-underground-entrance-94193/">https://pixabay.com/en/cave-tunnel-underground-entrance-94193/</a></li> </ul> 
